data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxury living! This newly renovated 6-bed, 3-bath gem stands as the crown jewel of the neighborhood, boasting an expansive 3360 sq ft. The open kitchen, adorned with quartz counters and a huge island is a culinary enthusiast's dream. Imagine yourself cooking and entertaining family and friends during the holidays here. Additional features include a versatile loft area that can also serve as a family room, an electric fireplace insert in the living room, vinyl floors throughout, a 1-car garage, a nicely landscaped yard, and 6 nicely sized bedrooms as well as a super unique style, this residence is sure to please.  Don't miss the chance to call this house a home!
